OL,5, US chat-show host Jon Stewart has      
OL,6, denied accusing Harry Potter author JK 
OL,7, Rowling of anti-Semitism in comments he
OL,8, made on a podcast last month.          
OL,10,FThe satirist compared goblins who run  
OL,11,FGringotts bank in the series of fantasy
OL,12,Fnovels and films to characters in a    
OL,13,F1903 anti-Semitic publication.         
OL,15,FHe has now said the conversation played
OL,16,Fon the podcast was meant to be "light  
OL,17,Fhearted" and he "does not think the    
OL,18,FHarry Potter movies are anti-Semitic". 
OL,20,FRowling has not responded.             
